display_long_description:
# Can you survive in a wild multiplayer horror game where monsters hunt you down? 

Whether you're hiding on a shelf, swinging a traffic cone, or sacrificing a friend to make it out alive, the fun never stops!

[media]
# A crazy survival challenge where monsters chase you and your friends!

[media]
# Unexpected twists in every map, you’ll have to stay alert!

[media]
# Customize your look and become the most stylish Baboon!

[media]
# Tons of awesome game modes and maps to explore!

[media]
**Play Scary Baboon today and test your survival skills!**

While you're at it, join thousands of Baboons in our Discord for updates, challenges, giveaways, and sneak peeks! 

# discord.gg/scarybaboon
